pageType: content
background:
  type: solid
  color: "$background"
elements:
  - elementId: accent-line
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [0, 0, 1280, 4]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$primary"
  - elementId: page-label
    elementType: text
    bounds: [60, 16, 200, 20]
    content:
      style: "$caption"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>RENCANA ANALISIS</p>
  - elementId: page-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [60, 50, 600, 40]
    content:
      style: "$title"
      fontSize: 28
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p><strong>Rencana Analisis</strong></p>
  - elementId: title-underline
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [60, 96, 80, 3]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$accent"
  - elementId: card1-bg
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [60, 120, 360, 340]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$surface"
    border:
      style: solid
      width: 1
      color: "$secondary"
  - elementId: card1-icon
    elementType: icon
    bounds: [80, 140, 36, 36]
    iconName: "fas:landmark"
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$primary"
  - elementId: card1-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [126, 140, 274, 36]
    content:
      style: "$subtitle"
      fontSize: 20
      color: "$primary"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p><strong>Latar Belakang</strong></p>
  - elementId: card1-text
    elementType: text
    bounds: [80, 190, 320, 250]
    content:
      style: "$body"
      fontSize: 16
      lineHeight: 1.6
      align: [left, top]
      text: |
        <p>Indonesia memiliki <strong>38 provinsi</strong> dengan data demografi dan ekonomi yang tersebar di berbagai sumber.</p>
        <p style="margin-top:10px">Diperlukan platform terpusat untuk analisis regional yang komprehensif dan terintegrasi.</p>
  - elementId: card2-bg
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [440, 120, 360, 340]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$surface"
    border:
      style: solid
      width: 1
      color: "$secondary"
  - elementId: card2-icon
    elementType: icon
    bounds: [460, 140, 36, 36]
    iconName: "fas:triangle-exclamation"
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$accent"
  - elementId: card2-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [506, 140, 274, 36]
    content:
      style: "$subtitle"
      fontSize: 20
      color: "$accent"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p><strong>Problem Statement</strong></p>
  - elementId: card2-text
    elementType: text
    bounds: [460, 190, 320, 250]
    content:
      style: "$body"
      fontSize: 16
      lineHeight: 1.6
      align: [left, top]
      text: |
        <p>Data <strong>PDRB</strong> dan <strong>populasi</strong> per provinsi (2019-2023) tersepat di BPS dan WikiData, sulit diakses secara terintegrasi.</p>
        <p style="margin-top:10px">Analisis perbandingan regional, tren temporal, dan ketimpangan distribusi memerlukan integrasi data.</p>
  - elementId: card3-bg
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [820, 120, 400, 340]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$surface"
    border:
      style: solid
      width: 1
      color: "$secondary"
  - elementId: card3-icon
    elementType: icon
    bounds: [840, 140, 36, 36]
    iconName: "fas:bullseye"
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$primary"
  - elementId: card3-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [886, 140, 314, 36]
    content:
      style: "$subtitle"
      fontSize: 20
      color: "$primary"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p><strong>Tujuan & Solusi</strong></p>
  - elementId: card3-text
    elementType: text
    bounds: [840, 190, 360, 250]
    content:
      style: "$body"
      fontSize: 16
      lineHeight: 1.6
      align: [left, top]
      text: |
        <p>Membangun platform <strong>Data Lakehouse</strong> skala Enterprise menggunakan:</p>
        <ul>
        <li>MinIO (Object Storage)</li>
        <li>DuckDB (Compute Engine)</li>
        <li>Arsitektur Medallion (Bronze-Silver-Gold)</li>
        </ul>
        <p style="margin-top:8px">Integrasi data dari WikiData dan BPS untuk analitik siap pakai.</p>
  - elementId: bottom-bar
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [0, 710, 1280, 10]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$primary"
    opacity: 0.1
  - elementId: page-number
    elementType: text
    bounds: [1200, 690, 60, 20]
    content:
      style: "$caption"
      align: [right, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>02</p>
